---
---
<section id="features" class="py-16 sm:py-24 px-4 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-title font-bold text-primary mb-4">
        Everything You Need to Get Accommodations That Work
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lead text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Built by employment lawyers and migraine sufferers — because "just a headache" is a real disability protected under ADA.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Value prop cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="group bg-surface rounded-2xl p-7 border border-border hover:shadow-card-hover hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/>
            <path d="M14 2v6h6"/>
            <path d="M16 13H8"/>
            <path d="M16 17H8"/>
            <path d="M10 9H8"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Templates That Speak Your Language</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Legal documents written specifically for migraine and cluster headache accommodations — not generic disability forms that HR hands you when they don't know what else to do.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="group bg-surface rounded-2xl p-7 border border-border hover:shadow-card-hover hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/>
            <path d="M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Evidence That Forces Them to Listen</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Generate documentation that proves the reality of your condition to employers. Finally have paperwork that says what you've been trying to tell them for years.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="group bg-surface rounded-2xl p-7 border border-border hover:shadow-card-hover hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Keep Your Job Without Losing Yourself</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Get the accommodations you need to stay employed — flexible schedules, lighting modifications, medication breaks — without having to quit or go on disability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
